      • deleteMachine

        public void deleteMachine(java.lang.String mode)
        This method delete a machine with a specific mode
        Parameters:
        mode - -machine: this just delete the file of config of the machine and the machine itself, no media will be deleted, the snapshot are not deleted -machineAndHardDrive: this delete the config files, the machine and the hard drives attached to the machine, the snapshot are deleted -machineAndHardDriveAndISO: this delete the config file, the machine, the hard drives and also the ISO attached to the machine, the snapshots are deleted
